/stat/type/class/race/etc. For example if you want to find all the bracers that a human cleric can where, you just choose Human, Cleric, and Wrist and it will tell you all items for sale that fit those requirements along with who is selling it and for how much. Then you can right click on the persons name in the box and it will give you directions on where they are (I found it very hard to find a particular &quot;vendor&quot; until I figured this out).<br>
